law.history: Repealed 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 371, sec. 64, effective July 15, 1996. -- Created 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 512, sec. 82, effective July 15, 1994.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Promotion of access to preventive health services by low-income Kentuckians through local health departments -- Cabinet to establish program as a provider of last resort.
